# Icon Placeholders

This directory should contain the following icon files for full SEO optimization:

## Required Icons:
- favicon-16x16.png (16x16 px)
- favicon-32x32.png (32x32 px)
- apple-touch-icon.png (180x180 px)
- android-chrome-192x192.png (192x192 px)
- android-chrome-512x512.png (512x512 px)

## Social Media Images:
- og-image.png (1200x630 px) - For Open Graph (Facebook, LinkedIn)
- twitter-image.png (1200x675 px) - For Twitter Cards
- screenshot.png (1280x720 px) - For structured data
- screenshot-wide.png (1920x1080 px) - For PWA manifest
- screenshot-mobile.png (750x1334 px) - For PWA manifest

## How to Generate:
Use the favicon.svg as a base and generate PNG versions:
1. Use a tool like https://realfavicongenerator.net/
2. Or use ImageMagick: `convert favicon.svg -resize 32x32 favicon-32x32.png`
3. Create screenshots of the actual app for social media images

The current favicon.svg uses the CollabCanvas brand color (#0ea5e9) with a
minimalist design representing a canvas with shapes.
